*Women&#x27;s Wrestling Hall of Fame
**Class of 2024
*World Wrestling Federation
**WWF Women&#x27;s Championship (1 time)
**WWE Hall of Fame (Class of 2006)
*Wrestling Observer Newsletter
**Manager of the Year (1991)

